# Secrets
.env

# Don't commit/republish full transcripts (Motley Fool ToS) -- they're a local cache
transcripts/

# Raw 8-K releases/supplements are a local cache too -- re-fetchable from EDGAR by URL
raw/

# Unpublished blog drafts -- keep these private until the post launches
outputs/blog_draft_*.md

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
